NAME

  **democurses** - test curses module

SYNOPSIS

    democurses 

DESCRIPTION

    Democurses is a test of the curses module. Curses are shortcuts that change
    text formatting, cursor location and the like. Click any key to move through
    the demonstrations.

OPTIONS

    -h, --help:  output usage information and exit

SEE ALSO

    [demoanim](/data/man/demoanim.dsmd), [demomarkdown](/data/man/demomarkdown.dsmd), [demomousetouch](/data/man/demomousetouch.dsmd)